    "Thanks for signing up! Before getting started, could you verify your email address by clicking on the link we just emailed to you? If you didn't receive the email, we will gladly send you another.": "感谢您的注册！在开始之前，请点击我们刚发送给您的邮件中的链接以验证您的邮箱地址。如果您没有收到邮件，我们很乐意为您重新发送。",
    "The extension checks the georeference.it API for that occurrence.": "扩展会为该记录查询 georeference.it API。",
    "The extension is open source. Bug reports, translations, and pull requests are welcome.": "该扩展是开源的。欢迎提交错误报告、翻译和拉取请求。",
    "The extension only sends the GBIF occurrence key (a public identifier) to our API. It does not collect, transmit, or store any personal information. Your panel position and size are saved locally in your browser only.": "该扩展仅向我们的 API 发送 GBIF 记录密钥（一个公开标识符）。不会收集、传输或存储任何个人信息。面板的位置和大小仅保存在您本地浏览器中。",
    "The extension panel appears automatically on GBIF occurrence pages, showing the suggested coordinates on a map and the current status — here, a pending suggestion for": "扩展面板会自动出现在 GBIF 记录页面上，在地图上显示建议坐标和当前状态 — 此处显示的是以下物种的待处理建议：",
    "The platform code is freely available on GitHub. Contributions welcome.": "平台代码已在 GitHub 上免费开放，欢迎贡献。",
    "There are suggestions to review. To place a new point, click": "目前有待审核的建议。要放置新的点，请点击",
    "These are all the specimens that share this locality description. Check or uncheck them to include or exclude individual records from your georeference.": "这些是共享该地点描述的所有标本。勾选或取消勾选可将各条记录纳入或排除在您的标注之外。",
    "This is a secure area of the application. Please confirm your password before continuing.": "这是应用程序的安全区域。请在继续前确认您的密码。",
    "This is the written locality description from the specimen label — the text you'll interpret to place a point on the map.": "这是来自标本标签的文字地点描述——您需要据此判断在地图上放置点的位置。",
    "This point looks far outside the expected area (county/state). Please double-check the coordinates, or explain in Remarks if the locality description is misleading.": "该点似乎远在预期区域（县/州）之外。请仔细检查坐标，如果地点描述有误导性，请在备注中说明。",
    "This point looks far outside the expected country. Please double-check the coordinates, or explain in Remarks if the locality description is misleading.": "该点似乎远在预期国家之外。请仔细检查坐标，如果地点描述有误导性，请在备注中说明。",
    "This point looks far outside the expected municipality. Please double-check the coordinates, or explain in Remarks if the locality description is misleading.": "该点似乎远在预期市镇之外。请仔细检查坐标，如果地点描述有误导性，请在备注中说明。",
    "This quick tutorial walks you through the main tools. You can reopen it at any time by clicking the ? Help button in the top-right corner of the map.": "这个简短教程将带您了解主要工具。您可以随时点击地图右上角的“?”帮助按钮重新打开它。",
    "Total": "总计",
